@startuml
title SageStore Runtime / Deployment Topology (Current Baseline)

node "Operator workstation" {
    artifact "SageStoreClient\nQt desktop app" as Client
}

node "Future consumer" {
    artifact "Web / Mobile / CLI /\nIntegration client" as OtherClient
}

node "Server host" {
    artifact "SageStoreServer\nBoost.Beast / Asio" as Server
    database "SQLite DB file" as Db
}

node "CI runner" {
    artifact "Jenkins pipeline" as Jenkins
    artifact "Local/VS Code docs task\nPlantUML + Doxygen" as DocsTask
}

Client --> Server : HTTP/JSON Dataset API
OtherClient --> Server : same API contracts
Server --> Db
Jenkins --> Server : configure / build / ctest
Jenkins --> Client : configure / build / unit tests
DocsTask --> Client : diagram + docs generation
DocsTask --> Server : diagram + docs generation

note bottom of Jenkins
Current automation gap:
docs rendering and packaging
are not enforced in CI yet.
end note

@enduml
